- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li>You should see an astrologer before using any astrological stones or equipment because you will have no idea how they will affect you.</li><li>You will not receive the finest results if you engage the services of two astrologers at the same time. One astrologer should be used at a time.</li><li>Keep in mind that, according to Vastu shastra, the kitchen should not be located in the southeast corner.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Sleeping on the metal cot is not recommended.</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li>Remove the mirror from your bedroom and replace it with an image of Lord Shiva and Goddess Parvati to avoid a late marriage.</li><li>So, in order to get married on time, you need to be aware of the following marriage-related factors. So, if you\'re having trouble getting married or with the sensation of love, you should call the astrologers from the website right away for any sort of astrological help because, according to our poll for the year 2021, Astrology Kart astrologer’s are the only one who can help you in this scenario. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/astrology-advice\">Astrology Advice</a></strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->', NULL, 'Miraculous tips for early marriage', 'Before getting married it is always said that couples always need to be protected from the evil eye as the elders say not to go outside so here astrologers give some tricks that they can follow.', 'Couple, married couple, kundli reading , astrology reading, new couple, wedding couple, astrology advices, astrologer advices', 1, 'miraculous-tips-for-early-marriage', 'kundli', 'Couple, married couple, kundli reading , astrology reading', '1636089008.jpg', 0, '2021-11-04 23:48:11', '2021-12-21 04:07:47'),
(10, '5 - Mahapurusa Yoga – an important combination in  Vedic astrology', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Yoga or unique combinations have a significant influence in a person\'s chart in Vedic Astrology. Such Yogas or combinations can help a person achieve success in life. Bring about significant growth and advancement in a person\'s life. A person might also obtain a lot of money and prosperity by participating in such fortunate Yogas.<br>Panch Yoga Mahapurush<br>Panch Mahapurush Yoga is one of the auspicious Yogas according to Vedic Astrology. Saturn, Jupiter, Mercury, Mars, and Venus are the five Tara Grahas that contribute to its formation. The Yogis are produced when one or more planets are exalted or in their own sign in the Kendra houses (1,4,7,10). It is a highly auspicious Yoga that makes a person affluent, renowned, and wealthy. Because of the Tara Grahas, the Panch Mahapurush Yoga is split into five sub yogas. Each yoga created by a certain tara Graha is given its own name. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk/astrologer\">Talk To Astrologer </a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4><br>Ruchika Yoga (Mars)<br></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Ruchika Yoga is one of the Panch Mahapurush Yogas, and it is generated by the planet Mars. When Mars is in its own sign (Aries or Scorpio) or in the exalted sign of Capricorn, it forms the Kendra Houses, which are the 1st, 4th, 7th, and 10th houses. A person born with Ruchika Yoga in his horoscope would be prosperous, well-known, intellectual, and bursting with excitement and vitality. The native will have an elegant demeanor, an appealing body, and a commanding demeanor. He or she will live a long and happy life.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4><br>Badra yoga (Mercury)</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><br>When Mercury is in the Kendra Houses, which are the 1st, 4th, 7th, and 10th houses in the sign of exaltation (Virgo), or in its own sign, Gemini or Virgo, Bhadra Yoga is created. At a young age, the native will be tall, handsome, learned, brilliant, intellectual, affluent, a good orator, sharp-witted, helpful, magnificent, and extremely well-known with a successful profession. It bestows intellect, reasonable thinking, decent speech, a good education, and business skills on its inhabitants. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/astrology-advice\">Astrology Advice</a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Hamsa Yoga (Jupiter)</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><br>When Jupiter is in Kendra Houses (1st, 4th, 7th, 10th), in its own sign (Sagittarius or Pisces), or in an exaltation sign, Hamsa Yoga is created (Cancer). The individual who does Hamsa Yoga will be tall and have a pleasing demeanor. He\'ll be gorgeous and appealing, with a pointed and raised nose. In life, natives receive love and respect, as well as popularity. The native has a strong personality and will be a person of integrity. Problems with the person\'s teeth may arise, and the teeth may be shattered at a young age.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4><br>MALAYA Yoga (Venus)</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><br>The planet Venus creates the Malavya Yoga when it is in the Kendra Houses, which are the first, fourth, seventh, and tenth in its own sign (Taurus or Libra) or in its exaltation sign (Pisces). Malavya Yoga gives a person a gorgeous face and huge eyes, as well as an appealing demeanor. He will be well-known, prosperous, and wealthy, possessing a large number of automobiles and other pleasures, as well as leading a successful life. It also teaches the natives strong acting abilities, dancing, theatre, and fashion. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat-with-astrologer\">Chat with Astrologer</a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4><br>Shasha Yoga (Saturn)</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><br>Another well-known Panch Mahapurush Yoga is Shasha Yoga, which is produced when the planet Saturn is in the Kendra houses, which are the first, fourth, seventh, and tenth in its own sign (Capricorn or Aquarius) or in its sign of exaltation (Libra). Shasha Yoga bestows a beautiful body, as well as a large number of servants, industries, and a happy and affluent existence. The individual will achieve enormous success in his life, but his growth will be gradual and trouble-free. It also bestows excellent health and moral qualities upon the native, as well as authority and rank.<br>Although having any one of the Panch Mahapurush Yoga in the Birth Chart is exceedingly fortunate and prosperous, we should be aware that having certain malefic planets with the Tara Grahas might negate the favourable Panch Mahapurush Yoga.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, '5 - Mahapurusa Yoga – an important combination in  Vedic astrology', 'Vedas are considered to be the way of living so Vedic astrology was built after reading all the Vedas. Here the astrologer\'s gains knowledge of astrology from reading the several planets and stars.', 'Yoga , Yogasnasas, meditation, fitness, Yogi, Suryanamaskar, Vedas , Vedic Astrology', 1, '5-mahapurusa-yoga-an-important-combination-in-vedic-astrology', 'vedic', 'Yoga , Yogasnasas, meditation, Vedic Astrology', '1636089031.jpg', 0, '2021-11-04 23:52:12', '2021-12-16 06:45:43');
