(11, 'Divine Vastu tips for happy married life', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Marriage is regarded as one of the most fortunate occasions in a person\'s life. The bond between a man and a woman, or between a husband and a wife, is extremely holy. It is also thought that matches are created in heaven, but in our physical sphere, efforts must be done to have a special attachment in the relationship. As a result, it\'s critical to keep track of this link. While they may have many differences, it is critical that they understand one another despite the disparities.<br>The path of life becomes less complex and more adventurous if the husband and wife maintain enough understanding. However, there are times when a partnership hits a tough patch and life seems hopeless. Furthermore, this relationship comprises not just two persons but also two families. As a result, even if things do not go as planned, both the husband and the wife must play their parts in changing and staying together.<br>Vastu Shastra, on the other hand, plays an important function in positively altering this connection. Furthermore, if necessary precautions are followed to develop a solid connection employing Vastu, the results will undoubtedly be fruitful!<br></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Divine Vastu tips</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>We\'ve given you some Vastu advice that will help you find devotion, joy, and prosperity in your married life. We should think of them in this light. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk-to-an-astrologer\">Talk to the Astrologer</a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Room\'s direction<br></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>You should position your bed in the house\'s southwest or northwest direction. This, it is thought, would keep the couple\'s love and resemblance alive. The direction of your room should be west, south, or south-west. This is where love and feeling triumph, solidifying your relationship.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>The room\'s lighting<br></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>If there is a light emission over the bed, it is considered ominous. According to Vastu, these light emissions disrupt your sleep and have a detrimental impact on the couple\'s well-being. The house\'s windows are blocking any light from reaching the bed. Place a drapery if it looks that it will be unavoidable.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Work In the room<br></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Avoid doing office work in the room if you don\'t want to harm your relationship with your spouse. Attempt to maintain as much tranquilly in your room as possible. If you usually do some extra work in the room, keep that in mind. Place your desks, pillows, chargers, and books in a separate room. These items have the potential to destroy your mood in the room. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat-with-astrologer\">Chat With Astrologer</a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Sleeping position<br></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Your head is in the south direction while you are resting. Room dividers should be painted in shades of blue, pink, yellow, and orange. Darker, dull, black, and cream shades should be avoided since they tend to make the space appear more harsh. There should be no mirror in front of the bed, according to Vastu Shastra. This can be extremely harmful to your health.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Wooden beds<br></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>According to Vastu, wood generates warm vitality, whilst metal beds generate chilly vitality. Wooden beds are always a good choice for a warm and inviting atmosphere in your room.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>Flowers and lamps in the bedroom<br></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Fresh blooms may infuse your love life with their scent. It will also eliminate the unpleasant odor from your room and create a pleasant atmosphere. Keep a safe space between you and the fake blossoms. Extravagant light shades will give the space a sensual feel and a sense of elegant curiosity. Green and blue colours are commonly used to improve one\'s mood. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/astrology-advice\">Astrologer Advice</a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, 'Divine Vastu tips for happy married life', 'As starting a new phase of life it is very important how the Vastu has been set so that their marital life would be blissful in every possible like the color, kitchen position, room\'s lighting, etc.', 'Married couple, Vastu tips, couple\'s room, New couple , astrology for new couple, couple horoscope, Vastu reading ,talk to astrologer', 1, 'divine-vastu-tips-for-happy-married-life', 'vastu', 'Married couple, Vastu tips, couple\'s room, New couple', '1636089012.jpg', 0, '2021-11-04 23:57:36', '2021-12-16 06:38:07'),
(12, '10 Ways to Incorporate Vastu in your Home', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>It is said that \"home is where the heart is.\" We desire to be at home, whether it\'s at the conclusion of a long day or first thing in the morning. A stay-at-home parent wants comfort, solace, and fond memories with his or her family. Because our house is so essential to us, we are often worried about protecting it from the negative energies that surround us. Each house has its own energy type, according to numerous traditional beliefs, however it is critical to have dwellings that radiate positive energy.<br>Here are some basic yet powerful techniques to help you protect yourself and your family from the negative aspects of life:</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4><br>The Entrance in the Correct Direction<br></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The main entryway is said to be the most important component of the house. When a house is built according to Vastu principles, it gives enormous happiness and wealth to everyone who lives there. The optimum entry direction is north or east, with the door opening towards the inside of the house.<a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/astrology-advice\"> <strong>Astrology Advice</strong></a><br></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\r\n<h4>The House\'s Color<br></h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Colors, like entrances, play an important function in boosting the optimism of your house. Use natural hues like white, green, and sky blue while painting your house. This will allow your home to absorb positive energy, which will benefit your entire family\'s health and well-being.<br>Every evening and dawn, light lights, Diyas, and incense at home. This acts as a cleanser and repels negativity as well as any evil eye.<br>Keep in mind that the kitchen should be constructed in the house\'s southeast corner. Another good choice is the northwest corner. Nonetheless, ensure that the gas stove is positioned to the southeast. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk/astrologer\">Talk to Astrologer</a></strong><br>Make your kitchen impervious to all ills. Always keep drugs out of the kitchen, as the kitchen denotes health and pleasure, whereas medicines denote the opposite.<br>There should be no mirrors in the bedroom, according to Vastu. If you have a dressing table or a mirror in your closet, you must cover it with a curtain while sleeping. Also, keep the mirror away from the bed, as it might lead to health problems and family strife.<br>Plants provide a lot of energy, but not all of them do it in a positive way. Avoid plants that produce milk within the home, such as cactus and rubber plants, as they disrupt the house\'s stability and harmony.<br>Use wind chimes as tinkling bells to assist break bad energy and allow positive energy to flow freely. They\'re also a lovely choice for house décor.<br>The holy emblem for riches and prosperity is Swastik. In-house use of Swastik symbols is recommended. Draw holy symbols such as Swastik and OM on the outside of your main entrance on a daily basis, and place Holy Water (Ganga Jal) in dark and disused parts of your home, changing it weekly.<br>Most individuals like storing superfluous items, however they not only take up room but also carry bad energy. So keep your house clean and clutter-free to attract positive energy and money into your home.<br>Because hardwood furniture is meant to provide harmony to the family, you should always prefer wooden furniture over new contemporary materials for your home. When the furniture is in regular shapes like rectangular, round, or square, it functions well.<br>*Bright colours produce happy feelings in the house. Brown and almond are good choices for the master bedroom. If you\'re freshly married, stay away from dark colours. Yellow, pink, and orange are happy colours that provide a calm environment. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat-with-astrologer\">Chat with Astrologer</a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, '10 Ways to Incorporate Vastu in your Home', 'Everyone is very particular about the interior designing in the house so they follow Vastu friendly design for an optimistic ambiance and there they choose the colors, kitchen areas, and many more,', 'colors in vastu , vastu, new home vastu, Vastu astrology, door mapping, architecture as Vastu, astrology reading, astrology advice', 1, '10-ways-to-incorporate-vastu-in-your-home', 'vastu', 'colors in vastu , vastu, new home vastu, Vastu astrology', '1636089016.jpg', 0, '2021-11-05 00:01:44', '2021-12-16 06:31:33'),
(13, 'अच्छी नींद के लिए 7 ज्योतिषीय उपाय', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>आज की भागदौड़ भरी और तनावपूर्ण दुनिया में लोग चैन से सो नहीं पा रहे हैं। इसका एक कारण उनकी बेहद व्यस्त दिनचर्या है, जिसमें रात में काम करना, मानसिक तनाव और देर रात तक मोबाइल या टेलीविजन देखना शामिल है। कई व्यक्ति अच्छी नींद के लिए भी दवाओं का उपयोग करके सोने के लिए पर्याप्त मजबूत होते हैं। हालांकि, इसका स्वास्थ्य पर नकारात्मक प्रभाव पड़ता है। एक व्यक्ति जो पर्याप्त नींद नहीं लेता है, उसे सफलता नहीं मिलेगी क्योंकि वह नींद से प्रेरित भ्रमों में बंद हो जाएगा और स्पष्ट रूप से सोचने में असमर्थ होगा।<br>रात की अच्छी नींद हर किसी के लिए जरूरी होती है। वह अपनी सुस्ती से छुटकारा पाता है, अपने शरीर को फिर से सक्रिय करता है, तरोताजा महसूस करता है, और जोश के साथ एक नए दिन से निपटने के लिए तैयार है। एक सर्वेक्षण के अनुसार, अनिद्रा दुनिया की 86 प्रतिशत आबादी को प्रभावित करती है। दौड़ने और तनाव के कारण नींद न आना हमारे दिन की सबसे बड़ी समस्या बन गई है। ज्योतिष शास्त्र के अनुसार, कुछ मंत्रों का जाप करने से आपको रात की शांतिपूर्ण और आरामदायक नींद मिल सकती है। इसके अतिरिक्त, आपका तनाव कम हो जाएगा, जिससे आप एक साफ स्लेट के साथ एक नए दिन की शुरुआत कर सकेंगे।<br></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>1</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><br>ज्योतिष शास्त्र के अनुसार यदि किसी व्यक्ति को सोने में परेशानी होती है तो उसे सोने से पहले हाथ-पैर धोना चाहिए और यह वाक्य रोज बोलना चाहिए। कुछ दिनों के बाद, आप देखेंगे कि आपको अच्छी नींद आ रही है।</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><br><strong>अगस्तीर्मघवश्चैव मुचुकुन्दे महाबल:<br>कपिलो मुनिरस्तिक: पंचाई सुखायिन:</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>2</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><br>यदि आपके पास भयानक सपने हैं जो आपको रात में कई बार जगाने का कारण बनते हैं, तो बिस्तर पर जाने से पहले अपने हाथ और पैर धो लें। इसके बाद दिन में 108 बार शांत मन से आसन पर बैठकर इस मंत्र का उच्चारण करें। ऐसा करने से आपको फिर कभी भयानक बुरे सपने नहीं आएंगे और आपका तनाव धीरे-धीरे दूर हो जाएगा।</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>वर्णस्य दक्षिण तू कुक्कुतो नाम वै द्विज:।<br>तस्य स्मरण दुःस्वप्न: सुखदो भावेत।</strong><br></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>3</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><br>ज्योतिष शास्त्र के अनुसार रोगी के सोने में असमर्थता अक्सर रोग के कारण होती है। ऐसा व्यक्ति पूरी रात करवट बदलने में बिताता है; ऐसे में इस मंत्र का जाप करने से रात को अच्छी नींद आएगी और समय के साथ बीमारी ठीक हो जाएगी।</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">जो लोग श्लोक का पाठ नहीं कर सकते वे केवल इन तीन मंत्रों को दोहरा सकते हैं…<br><strong>गोविंदाय नमः, अच्युतय नमः और अनंताय नमः</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>जो लोग इस मंत्र का उच्चारण कर सकते हैं उन्हें महत्वपूर्ण लाभ मिलेगा।</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>अच्युतनंत गोविंदा<br>नश्यंति सकल: रोग: सत्यं सत्यं वदम्यं।</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>4</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><br>रात को सोने से पहले लुटेरों या डकैतों के आने की आशंका रहती है। नतीजतन, व्यक्ति ठीक से सो नहीं पाता है, और एक समय के बाद, पलकें खुलती रहती हैं, जिसके परिणामस्वरूप पूरी रात इसी तरह व्यतीत होती है। यदि आप सोने से पहले घर की सुरक्षा करते समय इस मंत्र का उच्चारण करते हैं, तो कोई भी लुटेरा या डकैत आपके घर के पास नहीं आएगा, और आप आश्वस्त महसूस करेंगे, जिससे आपको अच्छी नींद आएगी।</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>आदिचौरकाफलास्य ब्रह्मदत्तवरस्य<br>तस्य स्मरण मात्र चारो की कामना नहीं।</strong><br></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>5</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><br>ज्योतिष शास्त्र के अनुसार कई बार आप दौड़ने और तनाव के कारण सो नहीं पाते हैं या आप अपने घर के अलावा कहीं और रहते हैं तो आपको नए क्षेत्र में सोने में परेशानी हो सकती है। ऐसे में अच्छी और सुखी नींद के लिए इस मंत्र का जाप करने से आपको अच्छी नींद आने में मदद मिल सकती है। पहुंचेंगे सोने से पहले इस दुर्गा सप्तशती मंत्र का 11 या 21 बार जाप करें। इससे रात को चैन की नींद आएगी। यह मंत्र उन लोगों द्वारा भी कहा जा सकता है जो रात की अच्छी नींद पाने के लिए अनिद्रा या मानसिक तनाव से पीड़ित हैं।</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>या देवी सर्वभूतेशु शयन-निर्माण संस्था।<br>नमस्‍य नमस्‍य नमस्‍तस्‍य नमो नम:</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>6</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><br>सोने से पहले अपने बिस्तर पर आंखें बंद करके और चौकस होकर बैठ जाएं और 5 गहरी सांसें लेने के बाद अपने मन में यह प्रार्थना करें: मैं शांत और संतुलित हूं। क्योंकि ईश्वर मुझमें विद्यमान है, मेरी सोच में कोई बेचैनी, चिंता या बुराई नहीं है। उसकी ताकत मुझमें काम कर रही है। किसी को भी मेरी शांति भंग करने की अनुमति नहीं है। यह प्रार्थना रोज रात को सोने से पहले करें। आपका दिमाग तुरंत साफ हो जाएगा और आप जल्दी सो जाएंगे।</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3>7</h3>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><br>अपनी आँखें बंद करो और अपने दिल में अपने भगवान से कहो, \"हे परमपिता, हम से दर्दनाक चीजें ले लो,\" रात को सोते समय। हमें केवल वही चीजें दें जो हमारे लिए सहायक हों, जो किसी भी कष्ट से रहित हों और जो हमें आध्यात्मिक संतुष्टि प्रदान करती हों। उसके बाद, वाक्यांश को सात बार दोहराएं।</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>मंत्र-<br>ओम विश्ववानी देव सवितु: दुरितानी पारा सुविधा याद भद्रम तन आ सुव।</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, 'अच्छी नींद के लिए 7 ज्योतिषीय उपाय', 'Everyone has sleep-related problems because of the lifestyle which is filled with stress or anxiety in return they have to face insomnia issues so here are some remedies that can reduce this issue.', 'अच्छी नींद , ज्योतिषीय उपाय, sleep, remedies, jyotish remedies, good sleep, Insomnia, Insomnia problems, mantras, मंत्रों का जाप', 1, '7-astrological-remedies-for-good-sleep', 'astrology', 'अच्छी नींद , ज्योतिषीय उपाय, sleep, remedies, मंत्रों का जाप', '1636113373.jpg', 0, '2021-11-05 06:32:12', '2021-12-31 00:29:30'),
(14, '22 Lucky things to keep at home as per Vastu Astrologers', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Astrology and vaastu are closely intertwined, keeping your home in a high-energy, joyful condition is crucial if you want to stay lucky. On our website Astgrologykart.com, you will find a few items that will assist you in balancing the Vastu components and boosting the energies.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Tortoise is number one.</strong></li><li>You can keep the tortoise sculptures in your home. It could be made out of metal, glass, or wood. If you need to get one for your home, Wednesday and Friday are the finest days to do it. To bring good luck, the tortoise figurine should be positioned towards the north or northwest direction.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Horseshoe 2</strong></li><li>A horseshoe is one of the most common things kept at the front door to bring in good luck. According to Vastu Shastra, a horseshoe at the entryway will bring good luck and fortune to the home. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat-with-astrologer\">Chat with Astrologer</a></strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Incense is being burned.</strong></li><li>Incense burning is a common practice in Indian homes and offices because it can help to cleanse negative energy from a space. However, you may not be aware of the best burning direction, how to correctly burn incense, or which mantras to sing while doing so.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Shells</strong></li><li>Keeping seashells in your home is also said to bring good luck and money. However, if the shell or Shankha cracks, this is a bad sign.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>A Hindu symbol is the swastika.</strong></li><li>If you have a painting or a figurine with a swastika symbol on it, it will bring good luck to your home. Vastu Shastra for the home covers a wide range of topics. There are several aspects to consider, like what to keep and what to throw away, which direction to sleep in or design the bedroom in, and so on.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Candles</strong></li><li>Candles, in addition to being beautiful, can improve the air quality in your home, which can be beneficial to your health.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Painting depicting good fortune</strong></li><li>Vastu artwork portraying a gorgeous image of a river, flowing water, or goldfish on the wall offers good luck and fortune to your home and life. The larger an artwork is, the more energy it attracts. The importance of natural light and fresh air is emphasised in Vastu principles. It brings wealth and prosperity to your home.</li><li><strong>Fortune gleams</strong></li><li>Sparkling clean windows and doors attract fresh and pleasant energy to your home and life. Create a little garden with a curved walkway outside the window, or pave the path with pebbles and add a fountain if you have the space. Maintain a constant flow of water in a water fountain on your property\'s northeast corner.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>The tranquil wealth wall</strong></li><li>Don\'t leave a wall exposed if the entrance has one. Loneliness is indicated by a naked wall, especially if it is near the entryway. It has a dismal and pessimistic tone to it. Use your imagination to decorate the wall.<a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk-to-astrologer\"> <strong>Talk to Astrologer</strong></a></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Fish:</strong></li><li>This is a potent wealth symbol. When placed in a clean tank, they bring wealth into your home. In a living area, an aquarium is ideal. Goldfish have traditionally been associated with good fortune.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Laughing Buddha:</strong></li><li>When placed in front of the main door, this muscular, happy-looking man brings fortune into your home. Choose from a choice of colours to complement your current decor.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Three-legged frog:</strong></li><li>More than one three-legged frog with a coin in its mouth can be found in your home. Place it under tables and chairs for the greatest effects.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Six-tiered water fountain:</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li>This is a lovely symbol of prosperity and opportunity, therefore place it in your home\'s north zone.</li><li>Plants: Plants with circular leaves are a great way to boost the value of your home. The vital energy of plants also cleanses negative energy. All you have to do is keep the leaves green and fresh all of the time. Lotus, water lilies, tangerines, and jade are just a few of the gorgeous plants that bring good luck. Make them the centre of attention in your room.</li><li>Sailing ships are a potent symbol of wealth. When they sail inside the house, they are thought to bring money with them. When properly organised, they can even appear majestic. You can have as many ships as you like in your home.</li><li>The presence of more than one ship could imply that you have many revenue streams.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Gem-bearing trees:</strong></li><li>These add to the room\'s richness element while also beautifying it. To make a statement, place them on your coffee table.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Birds:</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li>Bird images are always a terrific way to bring positive news into the home. At all times, make sure they\'re flying in and not out.</li><li>COLOR Feng shui assigns meaning to the colours that are utilised in the residence. The colour green conjures up images of nature, whilst the colour yellow conjures up images of force.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Declutter</strong></li><li>One of the easiest feng shui rules to follow is getting rid of clutter in the foyer of your home. This is not to say that you should add anything to your home, make any changes, or give it a dramatic makeover. All you have to do now is pick up your belongings from the floor. Maintain order by keeping everything in its rightful place. If you have enough space to move around, you\'ll feel more at ease and be able to think more clearly.&nbsp;</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Platter of Fruit</strong></li><li>A citrus-based dish with pomegranates or juicy grapes appears to be rather appetizing. It can be used to ward against bad luck and bring prosperity and positive energy into the home. They indicate affluence as well as improve general health when put in the kitchen, which is a symbol of prosperity in feng shui. It definitely belongs among the items that offer good luck to your home! Don\'t be afraid to try it; you won\'t be disappointed!</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Bamboo can be utilized as a decorative element.</strong></li><li>Bamboo is often recognised as one of the most powerful good luck charms in a feng shui home. It\'s a hydroponic plant that can provide peace and luck to any location, as well as a better mood and enhanced productivity.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Furniture that has been well-organized</strong></li><li>It\'s been suggested that arranging your living room furniture in a circular manner allows for improved energy flow. If the bed is strategically placed diagonally from the bedroom entry, good energy is thought to be brought in more. The appropriate kind of furniture is one of those items that might offer good luck to your home. As a result, use caution when using it! <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/astrology-advice\">Astrology Advice</a></strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->', NULL, '22 Lucky things to keep at home as per Vastu Astrologers', 'Everyone follows the traditional concept after looking to the Chinese astrology called Fengshui as this is the new trend so everyone wants a Vastu-friendly home because of positive surroundings.', 'Vastu, Vastu reading, astrology reading, prediction, prediction for new home, new home Vastu, astrology advice for new apartment, rented apartment vastu', 1, '22-lucky-things-to-keep-at-home-as-per-vastu-astrologers', 'vastu', 'Vastu, Vastu reading, astrology reading, prediction', '1636089019.jpg', 0, '2021-11-05 06:39:43', '2021-12-21 04:11:11'),
