(20, 'The Power of Astrology in Bringing Financial Freedom and Wealth Abundance', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>We focus all of our efforts on achieving financial independence from the moment we are adults. Since we were in school, we have focused our efforts on obtaining a job that will give us a steady stream of money.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Given the importance of cash in a person\'s life to ensure smooth survival in today\'s materialistic, money-driven world, this is totally acceptable.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The social prescription for making a lot of money in life is \"hard labour.\"</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Hard work is undoubtedly essential to obtain anything good in life.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Simply look around the world and count the number of people who work nonstop, day and night, and still manage to make ends meet, or, to put it another way, who are scraping their way through life\'s harsh realities!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>What is the rationale for this?</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Hard work alone will not bring you success and happiness in life because other factors play a major and, to be honest, a large role in shaping a person\'s fate.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Our financial position is being decoded through Vedic Astrology.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>According to the website astrologykart.com, Vedic Astrology is a science that reveals what the planets have in store for us in different facets of our lives.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Planets give us results in various areas of our lives based on our karmic account from previous lives. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat-with-astrologer\">Chat with Astrologer</a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The type of karmic structure that is unfolding from our karmic account at any one time in our lives determines the type of consequences.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>When our positive karmas are unfurled, we have positive results, and when our negative karmas are unfurled, we have problems in life. Vedic Astrology gives strategies for interpreting a horoscope to understand how and when planets in the horoscope affect various elements of the native\'s life.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>As a result, we have the choice of incorporating certain extremely powerful astrological treatments into our life in order to cancel or reduce the unfavourable planetary impacts that we are currently experiencing or will encounter in the future.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>We need to have our horoscopes reviewed by a qualified astrologerkart.com.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>An astrologer\'s primary goal is to correctly identify what different planets mean for a native\'s financial domain and when they are casting their respective influence on the native\'s financial domain so that timely remedial measures can be taken to mitigate the negative effects of ill-placed planets and maximise the positive effects of well-placed planets in the native\'s finance horoscope. If you\'re lucky enough to be able to have a consultation with an astrologer.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The Houses in our Finance Horoscope that have the greatest influence on our financial situation!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>An astrologer generally examines the state of the following houses from a financial aspect when projecting a native\'s fortune based on his or her date of birth and other natal data:</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>House No. 2</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This house represents \"Accumulated Wealth and Bank Balance.\"&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>To have a stable and excellent financial condition in life, this house must be strong and free of any negative influences.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>6th House</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This home\'s theme is \"Job and Competition.\"</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Those&nbsp; hunting&nbsp; for work or preparing for competitive tests need a strong and positive 6th house.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Furthermore, because this house represents rivalry, its strength becomes even more significant when it comes to promotions and job progress.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Even for individuals who own their business, competition is a constant concern that keeps people on their toes and dictates their profit margins. As a result, even self-employed people need the help of a strong 6th house in order to optimize their earnings.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>The House of the Seventh is a house in the United States that was founded in 17</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This house represents \"Business and Partnerships.\"</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>For obvious reasons, a self-employed person requires a positive &amp; only positive 7th house if he or she wishes to run a successful business in today\'s world of fierce rivalry in every industry. Any negative impact on this house would result in unneeded hurdles and regulatory challenges, as well as regular economic interruptions.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>When all parties involved have a good 7th house in their horoscopes, they make successful commercial connections. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk-to-astrologer\">Talk to Astrologer</a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>No. 8 is a house in the United States.</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The emblems for this house are \"Obstacles, Sudden Gains/Losses, and Inheritance.\"</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>A one-time windfall gain can improve a person\'s financial status, while a one-time financial setback can bring that native\'s financial graph to a halt.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>As a result, it is vital to pay attention to the 8th house, even if it does not indicate any immediate financial rewards.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>It\'s also worth noting that the 8th house offers all the answers for those wondering if they\'ll obtain the inheritance they deserve.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>No. 10 is a house in the United States.</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This house represents \"Career, Profession, Name, Fame, and Position.\" This house defines the level to which people who work or live in the public eye will rise, as well as the position they will hold in their chosen field. Furthermore, the state of your horoscope\'s 10th house impacts the extent to which your company\'s brand will be recognised.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>The 11th House of Representatives is a legislative body of the United States.</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This house indicates \"Gains and Realization of Desires.\"</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This house\'s strength decides whether or not your dreams come true in your life.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>To put it another way, if you want to live a lavish life, you need a lot of planets in the 11th house that are profitable at all times or at least most of the time.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>This house represents House No. 12 \"Expenditures.\"</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Now, in a person\'s horoscope, this house must be well balanced because expenditures are necessary not only to ensure survival and have needed objects in life, but also to provide numerous comforts and conveniences.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>If a person\'s spending exceeds his or her income, he or she will eventually run into financial difficulties.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>As a result, the situation of the 12th house in terms of an individual\'s wages must be perfectly balanced.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>A Remedy that Ensures Unexpected Prosperity in Life! Vedic Astrology presents various truly effective treatments for gaining money and settling finances in life based on the particular planetary conditions in a native\'s horoscope.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>In contrast, a Sri Yantra is a treatment that ensures the flow of lucky energy in one\'s life.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Consult a reputable astrologerkart.com to learn the exact will of the planets for you and how you may use luck to your advantage!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Astrology Kart provides a highly useful Financial Status Astrology Report that reveals what the planets have planned for your financial future and recommends vital cures to assure wealth and prosperity in your life. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/astrology-advice\">Astrologer Advice</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, 'Power of Astrology in Bringing Financial Freedom of Abundance of Wealth', 'In Astrology Kart the astrologers suggest what are the ways that will bring abundance in the business or the career of people. Astrologers give some tips that can sideline all debris in their career.', 'abundance of wealth, financial astrology, finance, astrology prediction, talk to astrologer, chat with astrologer, astrologer advice, prediction related to career', 1, 'power-of-astrology-in-bringing-financial-freedom-of-abundance-of-wealth', 'business', 'abundance of wealth, financial astrology, finance, astrology prediction', '1637065838.jpg', 0, '2021-11-16 07:00:57', '2022-01-22 00:42:44'),
(21, 'Your guide to astrology and COVID-19', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Astrologykart.com</strong>, The Corona Virus has made living extremely difficult in today\'s world. It has been linked to serious acute respiratory issues in the past. It\'s a highly contagious disease that spreads through human contact or proximity to an affected individual. It may result in the patient\'s death (mortality rate is just 3 percent ). This infection, along with the terror, has expanded fast in recent weeks. With the closure of schools, colleges, movie theatres, and even most countries\' borders to outsiders, markets have become barren. We reasoned that Astrology would be able to shed some light on this circumstance, which has left us socially and spiritually crippled.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The first coronavirus case was discovered in the Chinese city of Wuhan at the end of 2019. More than 3000 deaths have been officially documented as a result of this virus, which has been detected in 80 countries so far. Novel CoronaVirus-19 is the scientific name for this deadly virus (COVID-19). The World Health Organization designated it a global public health emergency on January 23, 2020, citing the rapidly increasing number of coronavirus cases. According to the official data, the Coronavirus has infected over 137 persons in India so far. The number of coronavirus cases, or people infected with the virus all across the world, has surpassed 1,89,683 with more than 7500 deaths. WHO, in collaboration with leading governments from around the world, is working hard to prevent the disease from killing additional people. The number, on the other hand, continues to rise.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Every sickness is caused as a result of various circumstances / planets being at a particular point in the transit, according to astrologykart.com. Each of us has a different constitution depending on our moon sign.