(48, 'The king of all planets - sun has just entered its sign of exaltation arise', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Astrologykart.com, The king of the planets, Sun, has just entered the fiery sign of Aries, which is also Sun\'s sign of exaltation. In the sign of Aries, the Sun becomes exceedingly powerful, as does its impact on the rest of the planet. So, what will the Sun\'s transit in Aries bring you from April 14th to May 15th, 2019?</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Aries&nbsp;</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• The Sun is the Lord of the 5th house in your natal horoscope and is currently traveling through the 1st house. The 5th house is generally about intelligence, speculation, and love, whereas the 1st house, or ascendant, is mostly about overall personality.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Chat with astrologer</strong>.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li>Astrologykart.com Sun is extensively pushing the possibility of landing a government job (if you are planning/preparing for one). Even if you work in the private sector, this transit of the Sun indicates an increase in your name and popularity, as well as a significant probability of a pay raise, promotion, or just higher officials recognizing and praising your work. In a nutshell, this Sun transit will be beneficial to you! <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/astrology-advice\">Astrology Advice</a></strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Taurus&nbsp;</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Sun rules the 4th house of your natal horoscope and is currently transiting the 12th. The 4th house is largely about comforts and conveniences, motherhood, vehicles, and property, whereas the 12th house is mostly about spending, overseas travels/settlement, and hospitalization.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;• You will see an increase in your spending. You can buy a house or a car during this time, and if you want to travel overseas, this transit of the Sun is very favorable. \"Beware of your adversaries, as they will be very busy at this period and will try to damage you,\" is the most essential message for you. Talk to the best astrology.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;• So stay away from confrontations and fights during this time, and keep your eyes and ears open.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Gemini&nbsp;</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• The Sun rules the 3rd house of your natal horoscope and is currently transiting the 11th. The 3rd house is primarily related to bravery, short journeys, and younger siblings, whereas the 11th house is primarily associated with gains and fulfillment of goals. This transit will be really beneficial to you, and you will be able to travel both locally and internationally as a result. You will amass a fortune as a result of your bravery and determination, and all of your travels during this period will be productive for you. Online chat with astrology&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>• </strong>Astrologykart.com, This travel, on the other hand, is detrimental to kids. If you are a student, you will find it difficult to concentrate on your studies at this time, and your efforts will not bring the results that you deserve. However, do not use this as an excuse to not work hard; instead, put up the best effort in your academic life. Pregnant women should take extra precautions because this transit is hazardous to their health. Chant the \'ShukraDev\' mantra to protect yourself and your unborn child from any negative impacts of the Sun\'s transit.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Cancer&nbsp;</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• The Sun is the Lord of the 2nd house in your natal horoscope and is currently traveling through the 10th. The second house is largely about speech, money, and family, but the tenth house is mostly about profession, name, and celebrity.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;• For you, the Sun will become \"Digbali\" and bring you great success. Your fortune is expected to expand significantly, and you will receive due respect from those in your profession or career. Your family, friends, and coworkers will all cheer you on in your endeavors.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• In terms of the downsides, your mother\'s health may deteriorate, so take care of her and repeat the \'ShukraDev\' mantra to shield her from the malefic consequences of this transit.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Leo&nbsp;</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• The Lord of the 1st house in your natal horoscope is Leo Sun, who is currently transiting in the 9th house. The first house is generally about personality, whereas the ninth house is mostly about spirituality, fortune, international adventures, and father.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;• During this transit, luck or fortune will be on your side, and you will succeed in any effort you undertake. There will be travels, and they will be helpful to the environment!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• The health of your younger siblings will be negatively affected by this transit. To alleviate the negative impacts of this transit on your siblings, offer \'Ardhya\' to \'Surya Dev.\'</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Virgo&nbsp;</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• The Lord of the 12th house of your natal horoscope is Virgo Sun, which is transiting in the 8th house. The 12th house is primarily connected with spending, foreign travel/settlement, and chronic illnesses, whereas the 8th house is primarily associated with age, hardships, in-laws, inheritance, unexpected gains, and accidents.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• During this season, the sun will protect you and help you live longer. Those who are afflicted will get alleviation, and their health will improve quickly. For you, the sun will form \'VipreetRajyog,\' bringing a boost in income and social respect. Expenditures will be reduced, and general health will improve dramatically. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat-with-astrologer\">Chat with Astrologer</a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Libra&nbsp;</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Sun rules the 11th house of your natal horoscope and is currently transiting the 7th. The benefits and realization of desires are primarily related to the 11th house, whereas the life-partner, business, and partnership are primarily associated with the 7th house.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p> • You will achieve tremendous success in your business and be able to produce cash in the manner that you desire. If you want to travel abroad, this time period will help you do so. Your health is a concern for you at this time, as it appears to be in jeopardy. </p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Make sure that you not only look after your own health but that you also look after the health of your spouse. This transit will be harmful to both of your health.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Scorpio</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li>Sun rules the 10th house of your natal horoscope and is currently transiting the 6th. The 10th house is generally about gaining reputation and renown, as well as career/profession, whereas the 6th house is mostly about ailments, loans, enemies, jobs, and competition.</li><li>Here, the Sun will provide relief from the symptoms that you have been experiencing as well as from the loan that has been worrying you. Your opponents will be destroyed by the sun, and if you are involved in a court fight, everything will turn out in your favor. However, if you experience a burning feeling in your eyes during this transit, see a doctor right away</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Sagittarius&nbsp;</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li>The Sun rules the 9th house of your natal horoscope and is currently traveling through the 5th. The 9th house is primarily related to spirituality and good fortune. The 5th house is primarily connected with intelligence, speculation, and love, while the 4th house is mostly associated with international journeys and fathers.</li><li>Your fortune will improve, and you will embark on rewarding journeys. If you\'re looking for work, this transport will assist you in finding one. If you\'ve put money into something, it\'ll pay off handsomely during this time, and your financial condition will be secure.</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Capricorn</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li>The Lord of the 8th house in your natal horoscope, Sun, is transiting in the 4th house. Age, hardships, accidents, and abrupt gains/losses are typically connected with the 8th house, whereas comforts, mother, property, and automobile are mostly associated with the 4th house.&nbsp;</li><li>Those of you who have been unwell will recover quickly, but your mother\'s health may decline, so take care of her. There will be volatility in your workplace, and you must exercise caution in terms of your job security. Offering \'Ardhya\' to Surya Dev and chanting \'Bajrang Baan\' are the best remedies for you.&nbsp;</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Aquarius&nbsp;</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li>The Sun is the Lord of the 7th house in your natal horoscope and is currently transiting in the 3rd. The 7th house is generally about marriage, business, and partnerships, whereas the 3rd house is mostly about courage, short trips, and younger siblings.</li><li>Your courage will grow, and you will see significant improvements in your business. Your life partner, as well as your younger siblings, will be supportive of you. In reality, you will receive support from everyone, including your spouse, friends, and family. However, you and your father may hold opposing viewpoints, which could result in a fight. So stay away from such things if you want to keep your relationship with your father pleasant.&nbsp;</li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Pisces&nbsp;</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li>The Lord of the 6th house of your natal horoscope is Pisces Sun, which is transiting in the 2nd house. The 6th house is generally about work, loans, litigation, and adversaries, whereas the 2nd house is mostly about money, speech, and family.</li><li>This is not a favorable time for you, particularly in terms of riches. During this time, refrain from lending or receiving money. Because of the harshness in your words, relations with family are likely to be rough during this passage. As a result, be careful not to say anything that can jeopardize your family\'s happiness. Keep your temper in check. When it comes to driving, you must use tremendous caution. </li><li>So this was the overall effect of the Sun\'s passage through Aries on persons born under all 12 Ascendant Signs. Astrology advice</li><li>However, we strongly advise you to schedule a personal appointment with one of Future Point\'s highly trained astrologers to learn the actual status of your natal horoscope and the implications of all planets\' transitory movements, both now and in the future.</li><li>A thorough horoscope analysis exposes the fundamental planetary difficulties that are plaguing a native, as well as exact corrective methods that can put an end to all afflictions and secure the native\'s success, money, and prosperity in life! <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk-to-astrologer\">Talk to Astrologer</a></strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, 'The king of all planets - sun has just entered its sign of exaltation arise', 'The king of the planets, the Sun, has just entered the fiery sign so the astrology kart astrologers predict which sign will be fine in this year 2022 and talk about the remedies related to the sign.', 'Sun, Planet Sun, Zodiac sign, zodiac for the planet sun, astrology of zodiacs, 12 zodiac signs, Talk to astrologer, chat with astrologer, astrology advice, planet that suits sun', 1, 'the-king-of-all-planets-sun-has-just-entered-its-sign-of-exaltation-arise', 'zodiac-signs', 'Sun, Planet Sun, Zodiac sign, zodiac for the planet sun', '1641622754.jpg', 0, '2022-01-08 00:52:01', '2022-01-08 00:52:01'),
(49, 'Astrology Kart Astrologers Predicts The Best Way To Choose Your Profession', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Astrologykart.com, Astrology is the study of planetary positions and the knowledge of malefic and benefic houses as well as Nakshatras (Constellation). Through the Job Horoscope, the native can learn about the career path he or she will take in the future.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list -->\r\n<ul><li><strong>Some significant elements to consider when deciding on a career path:&nbsp;</strong></li></ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• The native\'s horoscope\'s 2nd, 6th, and 10th houses reveal all about their income, career, working hours, and other connected facts.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Planets such as Jupiter, Mercury, and Saturn are associated with education, intelligence, and comprehension levels, among other things.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p> • The location of the Sun is crucial in determining whether or not the native will have a bright and prosperous career. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/astrology-advice\">Astrology Advice</a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;• Planet Saturn is recognised as a fair planet since it rewards you based on your level of effort. If you work hard at your job, you will undoubtedly see positive outcomes and may even get promoted to higher positions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• The riches of an individual is represented by the planet Jupiter. It also reveals whether or not a person will pursue a respectable career path.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;• If a native achieves success in a field that is linked to accounting or statistics, the Mercury planet is to blame. </p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Astrologykar