(91, 'What made Lata Ji the legend in Art Field?', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The “Swarkokila” of Bollywood who is the most respected Indian playback singer as well as earned the highest civilian award is no more. She has recorded songs in 36 languages and numerous foreign languages. Ms. Mangeshkar took her last breath at the age of 92 on Sunday morning at Breachcandy Hospital in Mumbai. For a few days, she was fighting from COVID-19. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk/astrologer\">Talk to Astrologer</a></strong>, from Saturday, her condition started deteriorating and was sent to ICU but she could not win the battle of life leaving a void in everyone’s heart.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Ms. Mangeshkar was the recipient of the highest civilian award i.e. Bharat Ratna, 2001, and also received the highest civilian honor of France in the year 2007. And this does not end here as she received Padma Bhushan, Padma Vibhushan, and Dadasaheb Phalke awards.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Coming from a musical family she used to compose music for many films also and was stated as “Nightingale of India”.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Lata Mangeshkar Kundli: What made her legend?</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Date of Birth of Lata Mangeshkar: 28 September 1929.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Birth Time: Unknown.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Place of Birth: Indore.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>In Lata Mangeshkar’s Kundli there she had a Mercury as Atmakaraka which is in Virgo that makes her Intelligent and efficient in her work. As Mercury is prominent similarly this makes her focused and down to earth. In the Amatyakaraka there is a Jupiter which makes her filled with wisdom and knowledge.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>What is Atmakaraka or Amatyakaraka?</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>In Kundli, Atmakaraka or Amatyakaraka is denoted by King or the advisor of the King which means that the person would be powerful with her thoughts and the history is proof itself that the advisor of the King is more powerful than the King. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat/astrologer\">Chat with Astrologer</a></strong>, in Lata Ji’s case, she is also considered to be powerful and visionary.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The Combination of Jupiter and the Amatyakaraka made Lata Ji’s career legendary, incomparable, and inspiring.&nbsp; The Zodiac Taurus was there in her Kundli which enhanced her artistic and creative side of her.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Though Lata Ji is not with us anymore, she will always be remembered for her impeccable contributions to music for eight decades. She has left a mark in this art field and the coming generation not only takes the learning but also take her footsteps of her to enhance the Indian culture. She will always aspire to the coming generation with her songs and her stalwart of Indian Culture.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Funeral with State Honors</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Swara Kokila Lata Mangeshkar left on her last journey on Sunday. She was cremated with state honors at Shivaji Park, Mumbai. During this, her sisters Usha, Asha, Meena were also present. Lata Ji\'s brother Hridaynath Mangeshkar lit the fire to her with moist eyes. Prime Minister Narendra Modi including people from many fields participated in sports, politics, and the entertainment world during the last journey of Lata Mangeshkar.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Bharat Ratna Lata Mangeshkar has forever merged with infinity by moistening the eyes of people across the country. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/\">Astrology Advice Online</a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, 'What made Lata Ji the legend in Art Field?', 'What made Lata Ji the legend in Art Field and why she is stated as the Nightingale by Voice. Know more about Lata Mangeshkar and the unknown facts of her Kundli.', 'Lata Mangeshkar, Nightingale of India, Lata Mangeshkar news, Kundli of Lata Mangeshkar, Narendra Modi, lata mangeshkar death date, Lata mangeshkar songs, lata mangeshkar latest news', 1, 'what-made-lata-ji-the-legend-in-art-field', 'current-affairs', 'Lata Mangeshkar, Nightingale of India, Lata Mangeshkar news, Kundli of Lata Mangeshkar', '1644216710.jpg', 0, '2022-02-07 01:22:02', '2022-02-07 01:24:42'),
