(93, 'Achala-Ratha Saptami 2022 : Significance of the Puja', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Achala-Ratha Saptami 2022: This year, Ratha Saptami is being celebrated with pomp in 2022. This day i.e. Achala-Ratha Saptami Tithi is already dedicated to the Lord Sun. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/\">Astrology Advice Online</a></strong>, On the day of Ratha Saptami, all the devotees try to please the Lord Surya Dev by their prayers. As per the mythology, it is believed that from the day of Rath Saptami or Achala Lord Surya Dev started giving knowledge to the world.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Which is also considered as the birthday of the Lord Sun.</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Among the devotees, this date is also considered the day of Surya Jayanti. This day is considered to be a very auspicious day to start a new work and the result on this day is always fruitful. To get rid of all the sins and sufferings from your life you must fast and worship Lord Sun and for this, you must know the auspicious time to worship, its importance, and remedy of Achala Saptami- Know the auspicious time of Achala Saptami</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"type\":\"1\"} -->\r\n<ol type=\"1\"><li>On the 7th of February Monday Achala Saptami is celebrated.</li><li> Snaan Muhurta on the auspicious occasion of Achala Saptami – to be done from 05.22 am to 07.06 am – Special duration – 01 hours 44 minutes</li></ol>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Achala Saptami is on the day of Arunodaya – 06.41 am</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Observable sunrise on the day of Achala Saptami – 07.06 am</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Saptami date starts – 07 February from 04.37 am</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Saptami date ends – 08 February till 06.15 am</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Significance of Achala Saptami.</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Bathing is considered to be very fruitful on the day of Rath Saptami or Achala or Arunodaya. Before sunrise, the Arunodaya period is usual for the four valleys. It is believed that all diseases will be destroyed if a person during Arunodaya takes a bath before sunrise. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk/astrologer\">Talk to Astrologer</a></strong>,  Because of this Ratha Saptami or Achala is considered to be Arogya Saptami.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Achala Saptami Puja Method</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>On the day of Achala Saptami, after taking a bath in Brahma Muhurta, take water in a pot and offer Arghya to Sun God by adding akshat, red flowers, and some grains of sugar. With a lamp of ghee, Lord Surya should be worshiped. There is a belief that if you will do this then Sun God will be pleased and bless you with good health and sanity mind. On the day of Ratha Saptami, all these measures should be taken.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>1. On the day of Achala Saptami, the yellow Kaner flower should be dedicated to the worship of Sun God, it removes all the troubles.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>2. If you are suffering from a financial crisis, then on this day red flowers of Kaner should be offered to the Sun God.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>3. It is believed that on this day if you offer red Kaner flower to the Lord Surya dev then there will be liberty from all the debt.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;4. Besides this, if the devotees feed jaggery to a red-colored cow then this will help the devotee to get progress in their business or job.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>5. If the donation is made by making a bundle of wheat and jaggery in red cloth, then it fulfills all the desires of the mind. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat/astrologer\">Chat with Astrologer</a></strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, 'Achala-Ratha Saptami 2022 : Significance of the Puja', 'Achala-Ratha Saptami 2022 has already started and many of the devotees know the Significance of the Puja but what is the best time to do the puja. Know more.', 'Achala-Ratha Saptami 2022, Surya Dev, Lord Sun, Surya Jayanti, puja of Achala-Ratha Saptami 2022, Surya puja, process of doing puja, puja time of Achala-Ratha Saptami, Ratha Saptami', 1, 'achala-ratha-saptami-2022-significance-of-the-puja', 'festivals', 'Achala-Ratha Saptami 2022, Surya Dev, Lord Sun, Surya Jayanti', '1644304877.jpg', 0, '2022-02-08 01:54:03', '2022-02-08 01:54:03'),
