(98, 'How to Prepare for Board Exam 2022?', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Board Exam 2022: After the release of the 10th and 12th datasheets by the CBSE Board, ICSE Board, State Boards have also released the datasheets of the 10th-12th examinations. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/\">Astrology Advice Online</a></strong>, after the release of the timetable for the board examinations, all the students have started preparing for the examinations. In such research, a surprising thing has come to the fore that children feel more stressed during the examination.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;This tension in children is not because they have to get ahead in the competition but because many wrong things happen around them and they become a part of it knowingly or unknowingly. Sometimes social media proves to be their biggest enemy, because on the one hand, while social media helps them in their studies, on the other hand, they also suffer from wrong information.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>So students need to learn the art of concentrating on their tasks which will prove helpful in their future and their career. So let\'s know how you can prepare well for board exams without any stress so that you can score good marks.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;1. Turn off Notifications:</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>First of all, you should turn off all your notifications (of social media), which are not useful for your study. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat/astrologer\">Chat with Astrologer</a></strong>, these notifications are for a few seconds but their effect is for a very long time. So we have to first make sure which notification is useful for us.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>2.</strong> <strong>Create Routines:</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>After that you make a routine chart of yours, make sure in it that what will be the time table of your study, by doing this you will be able to utilize your time, solve problems and concentrate on studies.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>3.</strong> <strong>Rank the Subjects:</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The third point is the most important, if you give equal time to all the subjects, then you will be able to understand in which subject you have to give more time so that your weak subject becomes strong. But at the same time keep in mind that it should not affect other subjects.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>4.</strong> <strong>Turn Off Multitasking:</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>When we work on different things at the same time, we may think that we are efficient but that is just our illusion. This is the reason for our mistakes and we destroy our creativity. So students should avoid multitasking and focus on one task at a time.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>5.</strong> <strong>Take the Time to Revise:</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This is the most important point, revision works as a panacea for any preparation. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk/astrologer\">Talk to Astrologer</a></strong>, Review everything you have studied and make sure you understand how much of the subject matter. In the end, study the topic on which you get stuck and understand all the topics very well.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, 'How to Prepare for Board Exam 2022?', 'As every student is very doubtful about their exams and CBSE and ICSE have already announced their Term 2 syllabus so how to Prepare for Board Exam 2022?', 'CBSE Term 2, CBSE Board Exam, ICSE Board Exam, Board Exam 2022, Student exam, Exam Preparation, Term 2 Syllabus, CBSE Board Exam 2022, ICSE Board Exam 2022', 1, 'how-to-prepare-for-board-exam-2022', 'current-affairs', 'CBSE Term 2, CBSE Board Exam, ICSE Board Exam, Board Exam 2022', '1644478606.jpg', 0, '2022-02-10 02:06:56', '2022-02-10 02:06:56'),
(99, 'What is the Significance of Sheetala Sashti?', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The marriage of Lord Shiva and Goddess Parvati, known as Sheetala  Sasthi or Sitala Sasthi, is celebrated in Odisha. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat/astrologer\">Chat with Astrologer</a></strong>, The date for Sheetala  Sasthi 2022 is June 5. Jyeshtha Shukla Panchami is the first day of the festival. Sambalpur, Odisha, hosts the most famous Sheetala a Sasthi Yatra (Sheetala  Sasthi Yatra).</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Lord Shiva signifies the blazing heat of summer, while Goddess Parvati represents the first showers. An extravagant wedding is thought to ensure a favorable monsoon.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Shiva Bibaha or Siba Bibaha is the first day of the celebration. Then there\'s the legendary Jatra, or Gods\' parade.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The festival is celebrated in rural villages as if it were a real wedding. The arrival of Shiva for the wedding ceremony, as well as the procession of the two deities, is a big deal.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The yearly Sheetala&nbsp; Sasthi Yatra event in Sambalpur, Odisha, commemorates Lord Shiva and Goddess Parvati\'s glorious wedding. Sambalpur, in the state of Odisha, is well-known for Shiva and Shakti worship. The \'Patra&nbsp; pending ritual kicks off the five-day celebration.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>After the death of Goddess Sati, Lord Shiva began to practice extreme austerity and lost interest in family life. Taking advantage of the situation, the demon Tarakasura appealed to Lord Brahma and was granted the boon that he would only be killed by Lord Shiva\'s son. Tarakasura wreaked devastation on the earth, heaven, and hell after acquiring the boon, and he expelled the \'devas\' from heaven.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>When the Devas contacted Vishnu, he informed them of the boon and advised them to seek Mother Shakti to discover a way out. Shakti agreed to marry Shiva and reincarnate as Parvati.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Shiva, on the other hand, continued to practice extreme austerity. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/\">Astrology Advice Online</a></strong>, Parvati, the daughter of Himalaya, only had Shiva on her mind and desired to marry him. Shiva, on the other hand, refused to accept her as his wife. Devas tried a variety of methods but were unable to persuade Shiva to change his views.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Finally, Parvati began serious meditation, and Shiva had no choice but to comply. (Women in North India and South India follow Hartalika Teej Vrat and Swarna Gowri Vratam, respectively, to obtain excellent husbands, as Parvati did.)</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The celestial pair wedded on Jyeshtha Shukla Panchami, and Kartikeya was born, who defeated the demon Tarakasura. This beautiful wedding is commemorated by the Sheetala&nbsp; Sasthi Yatra festival. During the celebration, a local family takes on the roles of Parvati\'s father and mother and proposes marriage to Shiva.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The parents accept Parvati as their daughter on Patra Pendi Day, on the first day of the festival. Goddess Parvati (temple idol) comes to her adopted parents\' house two days later.The bride is carried in a spectacular parade from her adopted house to the wedding celebration, which takes place at night.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Equally, Lord Shiva, the bride, arrives at the wedding ritual among other Hindu gods and goddesses. The celestial procession is led by Lord Hanuman and Narasimha. For the divine wedding, all of the traditions that are part of a conventional marriage in Odisha are followed.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The holy couple goes on a quest to the town of Nagar Parikrama the following evening, which is known as the \'Sheetala&nbsp; Sasthi Yatra.\'</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The wedding of a significant number of Servants or Hijras is another highlight of the festival. They claim they\'ve come to celebrate Shiva\'s marriage to Ardhanarishwara, who is half man, half female.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Because the wedding occurs during the start of the monsoon season, the festival is also known as Shiva and Parvathi\'s monsoon wedding. The severe asceticism practiced by Shiva is figuratively mirrored by the searing heat of July. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk/astrologer\">Talk to Astrologer</a></strong>,<strong> </strong>Shiva is soothed by Parvathi, the monsoon showers. Farmers use this exquisite wedding to commemorate the coming of the monsoon.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, 'What is the Significance of Sheetala Sashti?', 'Many festivals are being celebrated during the Magha month but one of them is Sheetala Sashti. Know what is the Significance of this festival Sheetala Sashti?', 'Sheetala Sashti 2022, Sitala shashti, Sheetala Sashti Vrata, Sheetala Sashti significance, Talk to Astrologer, Astrology Advice online, Consult an Astrologer', 1, 'what-is-the-significance-of-sheetala-sashti', 'festivals', 'Sheetala Sashti 2022, Sitala shashti, Sheetala Sashti Vrata, Sheetala Sashti significance', '1644567399.jpg', 0, '2022-02-11 02:46:53', '2022-02-11 02:53:38'),
(100, 'What Promises Should a Couple make on Promise Day?', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The festival of love lasts for a whole week from 7th to 14th February. In this, Promise Day is celebrated on 11th February. It is a day when you make a promise to your partner that you will remove all the troubles from the path of love and will stand together in every situation. Pledge to give him/her every happiness in the world. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/\">Astrology Advice Online</a></strong>, All these things are real and these thoughts generally come into every lover’s mind.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>On the occasion of Promise Day, make a genuine promise to your love that you can keep. This will make your relationship stronger. Amid raging love, don\'t brag at all! You might be seen throwing because this will not develop your impression. What our astrologer has to say about the things to be kept in mind while making promises in love?</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Love\'s Promises and their Breaking</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Astrology kart Astrologer says that if you want a smooth relationship with your partner then you must keep that kind of promise that eventually you can fulfill looking upon your conditions. Never try to make a false promise which you cannot fulfill or else the relationship comes to a conclusion where there is only one thing left i.e. breakup. When promises break a point of time comes where your partner ends up the relationship and after that, you have to go through several emotional breakdowns that gradually manifest to several kinds of mental health issues i.e. depression or anxiety.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>When the Heart is True</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Astrology Kart astrologer shows the ways to solve the problems in the relationship between boyfriend-girlfriend, husband-wife, parents, and children, sees many such cases every day, in which due to false promises so by this rifts start among the partners and the other partner feels cheated. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk/astrologer\">Talk to Astrologer</a></strong>, In this situation, there is a communication gap that gets increased over time in a relationship. Astrologer says that your partner and your family are happier than your promises because of what your feelings are.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Always look up to your intentions and what you want to do for them. For a while, you will enjoy all the big things but later you will feel suffocated or your partner might get pessimistic about you that you are not fulfilling your partner’s wish what he/she is saying. This creates mistrust in relationships.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Do this work on Promise Day</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• If you believe in this tradition of making a promise which is to be followed then make a promise to your partner on Promise Day. Your partner will also like this if you are comfortable in making all these promises.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>•We will always try to respect each other’s space and needs that make them happy.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Together we will move forward in life and will find time for our relationship between work.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Together we will work to achieve our dream into success and understand each other’s priorities as well as responsibilities.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Will be the holding each other’s hand firmly at every problem or happiness in life.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• These promises will genuinely increase the trust and compassion towards each other in the relationship by which love and respect towards each other also increase.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• If we are not on the same page or there is any kind of misunderstanding between us then we will communicate with each other to solve the matter. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat/astrologer\">Chat with Astrologer</a></strong>, Do not prioritize someone else’s thoughts in your relationship as this is your relationship.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, 'What Promises Should a Couple make on Promise Day?', 'Valentines week is being celebrated & every couple is trying their level best to impress their partners. So, what Promises Should a Couple make on Promise Day?', 'Promise day 2022, Happy Promise Day. Happy Promise Day 2022,  Promises, promise day status, promise day images, Promise Day quotes, Valentines week 2022', 1, 'what-promises-should-a-couple-make-on-promise-day', 'current-affairs', 'Promise day 2022, Happy Promise Day. Happy Promise Day 2022, Promises', '1644567721.jpg', 0, '2022-02-11 02:52:17', '2022-02-11 02:56:25');
