(125, 'Maha shivratri 2022: When is the auspicious time to worship in Mahashivratri?', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Mahashivaratri is a Hindu festival that takes place on the Chaturdashi date of the Krishna Paksha in the Falgun month.<a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat/astrologer\"> <strong>Chat with Astrologer</strong></a>, The Chaturdashi Tithi will begin at 01:59 a.m. on February 28 and will last until 12.17 p.m. on March 1st.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The festival of Mahashivratri is most fruitful at night, hence it will be celebrated with great pomp and gaiety on March 1, the most important festival of worshipping Devadhidev Mahadev. Lord Shiva will be honored and wooed by keeping Jalabhishek, Dugdhabhishek, Rudrabhishek, and Jagran.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Married women and unmarried girls will worship Shiva to boost their good fortune and find a suitable and desired life partner. On this day, the Chaturdash Linga will be worshipped.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>At midnight, Lord Shiva is said to have appeared in the form of a linga from a part of Brahma Ji. Bhole Nath is said to have wedded Gaura Mata on this day in several areas.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>All of the requests will be granted if Lord Bhole Nath is worshipped on this day by law. This time, Shani Dev will be in his own sign of Capricorn, Mars will be in his exalted sign, Guru and Sun will create Guruaditya Yoga, and Venus, the planet of prosperity and wealth, will also be there as a friend, enhancing the favorable results of the day.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>And then there\'s the one that makes all of your wishes come true. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk/astrologer\">Talk to Astrologer</a></strong>, All requests can be granted, according to astrology, provided specific measures are