o is holding a gold coin in one hand and a fan in the other, brings wealth to the home. Apart from that, keeping the Laughing Buddha on the boat on the workplace table is fortunate, but keep in mind that the boat should be maintained in such a manner that it can be seen entering the office.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Disease address</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>If someone in your house is unwell, but no test can determine what the ailment is, a Laughing Buddha holding a wu lu should be placed near the sick person\'s pillow. In the inquiry, his condition will be revealed soon. The yellow-colored Wu Lu is a variety of Chinese fruit.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Laughing Buddha sitting on a dragon</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>If you suspect that someone is performing magic in your home or that someone has cast an evil eye on your family, keep Laughing Buddha, the Lord of Divine Powers, perched on a dragon, in your home.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Precautions</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Laughing Buddhas come in a variety of shapes and sizes, each of which fulfills a distinct goal. Laughing Buddha may be kept anyplace in the house or workplace, but there are certain measures to take.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Don\'t keep it here</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Laughing Buddha can be placed anywhere, however, they should never be placed on the ground. Keep them in the same place of worship where God is preserved. These can be displayed in the living room for visitors to view. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat/astrologer\">Chat with Astrologer Online</a></strong>, Never keep a Laughing Buddha in the bath