f the same thing and patriots are often called mad by people.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, 'Shaheed Diwas 2022: Why Bhagat Singh, Sukhdev, and Rajguru sacrificed their life for the country on 23 March 1931?', 'Shaheed Diwas 2022: Bhagat Singh, Sukhdev, and Rajguru sacrificed their life for the country on 23 March 1931, know some of his inspirational thoughts.', 'Shaheed Diwas 2022, Bhagat Singh, Sukhdev, Rajguru, Shaheed Diwas,  23 March 1931, thoughts, inspirational thoughts, images of Shahid Diwas, Quotes by Bhagat Singh, Shaheed Bhagat Singh', 1, 'shaheed-diwas-2022-why-bhagat-singh-sukhdev-and-rajguru-sacrificed-their-life-for-the-country-on-23-march-1931', 'current-affairs', 'Shaheed Diwas 2022, Bhagat Singh, Sukhdev, Rajguru', '1648020287.jpg', 0, '2022-03-23 01:56:04', '2022-03-23 02:04:35'),
