(167, 'If your Child Struggles To Concentrate at Studies, try these Remedies', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Vastu Tips for Kids Room:</strong> Children have complete control over their minds. Every youngster has a specialty as well as likes and dislikes. Some children are so bright that they are usually visible in copybooks. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk/astrologer\">Talk to Astrologer Online</a></strong>, At the same time, some youngsters flee when they hear the word \"education.\" His concentration is not on his schoolwork. Such children divert their attention away from their schoolwork.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Children\'s focus has suffered as a result of the corona outbreak. They can, however, direct their attention to studies by using Vastu and Astrological treatments. Candles in the children\'s room are one of the cures. Please tell us which direction candles should be put in the children\'s rooms to keep their minds focused on their studies. Know additional astrological cures to help youngsters focus on their schoolwork.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Children are drawn to studies and feel engaged in studies when a candle is lit in the eastern, north-eastern, or southern region of their room. At the same time, their mental ability grows.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Which way should the candle not be lit?</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>So far, we\'ve discussed where candles can be put. However, there are specific areas where candles should not be burned. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/\">Astrology Advice Online</a></strong>, Placing a candle in the north direction of the house, for example, obstructs the arrival of money and can also damage the financial status of the property. As a result, candles should not be lighted in the north corner of the home.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Do not place the candle in this direction</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Candles should not be put in the house\'s northwest corner. In this case, candles, that is, placing a candle, causes tension among family members and a feeling of jealously towards family members in the mind.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions of the study table and chair</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The study table should be rectangular in shape. Although irregular form may appear appealing to some, it hinders attentiveness in studies. If possible, arrange the table so that the youngster does not face the wall. Make sure the chair\'s back is likewise sturdy.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Astrological practices to improve focus&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>• </strong>Astrology says that in addition to burning a ghee lamp in front of an image of Lord Vishnu, providing water to the banana tree and applying tilak on the kid from the soil there is also good.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>• </strong>According to astrology, if your child does not want to study at all, but a little piece of alum in his pocket and apply saffron tilak to his forehead and navel on a daily basis.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• It is also regarded good to offer religious books and pens at the shrine of Lord Vishnu on every Thursday in order to promote the child\'s enthusiasm in learning.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Your child\'s study table should always face east or north in the room where he studies.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Prevent youngsters from eating in bed, since this can lead to terrible nightmares and negative energy. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/chat/astrologer\">Chat with Astrologer Online</a></strong>, Children should not be allowed to eat on the bed since it is a place for rest and relaxation. </p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Avoid putting too many electronic equipment in a child\'s room, according to Vastu, because they cause significant electromagnetic stress and hazardous radiation. This might have a detrimental impact on a child\'s ability to concentrate.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Astrologers advise using light green or light yellow colours in the room to brighten the area and regulate mood swings. Avoid using black and blue bed sheets, carpets, and wallpaper, among other things, as they might elicit negative feelings in a youngster.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Unused stationery, such as pens without refills, unsharpened pencils, damaged books, old books, or newspapers, among others, generates bad vibrations, according to Vastu principles. To clear the route to achievement, the study table or desk should be clutter-free. Avoid putting shoes or slippers under the table since it interferes with focus.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Wild animal soft toys should be kept out of a child\'s room since they encourage violence in children.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• According to Vastu, children should avoid sleeping underneath a direct beam or an underground wardrobe since it causes stress and worry.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', NULL, 'If your Child Struggles To Concentrate at Studies, try these Remedies', 'If your child struggles to concentrate at Studies, try these Remedies; the result will be positive. seen. Vastu for Kids Room', 'Vastu for Kids Room, vastu, vastu tips, vastu shastra tips, vastu shastra for home, vastu for home, vastu for money, vastu dosh, vastu remedies for peace at home, vastu and kids, vastu and children room,', 1, 'if-your-child-struggles-to-concentrate-at-studies-try-these-remedies', 'vastu', 'Vastu for Kids Room, vastu, vastu tips, vastu shastra tips, vastu shastra for home', '1655891053.jpg', 0, '2022-06-22 05:17:57', '2022-06-22 05:17:57'),
(168, 'Sawan 2022: These zodiac signs will receive special Lord Shiva blessings during Sawan, know when it will happen on Monday.', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This year, Sawan will take place from July 14th to August 12th. According to astrology, the following zodiac signs will receive particular Shiva blessings in Sawan this time.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Sawan 2022: </strong>Sawan is a highly sacred and important month for worshipping Lord Shiva. During the whole Sawan Month 2022, Shiva worshippers worship Bholenath with complete devotion and commitment. According to Hindu tradition, Shiva worship practiced in the month of Sawan (Sawan Maas 2022) yields many times more crops. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/\">Astrology Advice Online</a>,</strong> This is why Shiva worshippers conduct Rudrabhishek of Lord Shiva on every Monday of Sawan. Sawan will take place this year from July 14th to August 12th.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>The 18th of July is the first Monday of Sawan (Sawan Somvar 2022). According to astrology, three zodiac signs in Sawan will receive special Lord Shiva benefits this year. Let us know which of the three zodiac signs will receive special Shiva blessings in Sawan, as well as when Sawan\'s Monday will fall.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>These three zodiac signs will receive special blessings from Shiva in Sawan</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Aries- </strong>According to astrology, those born under this sign might gain special Shiva blessings if they do special Shiva worship at Sawan. With Bholenath\'s support, there is a strong possibility of improving the financial side. Job and commercial prosperity are possible with Bholenath\'s blessing.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Gemini - </strong>People born under this sign might also benefit from worshipping Shiva in Sawan. People born under this sign will be able to excel in the field of career and all credit goes to the blessings of Lord Bholenath. Aside from that, practicing Rudrabhishek in Sawan can provide further benefits.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Capricorn - </strong>According to astrology, the people of Capricorn will be favoured by Lord Shiva in Sawan. Bholenath\'s special blessings can be received by consistently presenting water to Shivling during Sawan. Job and commercial advancement are possible with Shiva\'s blessing.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Dates for Sawan Somvar in 2022</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Sawan month starts on July 14, Friday.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Sawan\'s first Monday begins on July 18, Monday.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Sawan\'s second Monday - July 25th, Monday</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Sawan\'s Third Monday - August 1, Monday</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>• Sawan\'s fourth Monday - August 8, Friday</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Follow these steps in Sawan, and all your wishes will come true.</strong></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Sawan, the holy month of Lord Bholenath, begins this year on July 14th, 2022. Which will end on the 12th of August, the day of Shravan Purnima. <strong><a href=\"https://astrologykart.com/talk/astrologer\">Talk to Astrologer Online</a></strong>, Let us inform you that you may accomplish your dreams by making certain modifications and doing some simple procedures in this Sawan Vastu.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><strong>Do this task daily in Sawan.</strong></p>\r\n<!